title.rendered: Lisbon Rectangle All Weather Dining Set – Side Chairs

content.rendered:
The Lisbon Rectangle All weather set is made up of our Lisbon Square table and side chairs.

Made up with a polypropylene, making it durable which is ideal for outdoor use as well as indoors. The chairs also stacks for ease of storage.

Perfect for all manner of commercial venues such as hotels, spa’s, coffee shops and alike. Ideal for outdoor venues.

In stock for immediate despatch.

CTAS Tested, Guaranteed for 5 years. Light resistant pigment. Anti static.

Table Dimensions: 1500x900mm, 740mm High. 15KG

Side Chair Dimensions: 580mm D x 440mm W x 880mm H x 450mm SH – 3.8KG ea
